<span class="displaytext"><b>for immediate release <br/> contact:</b> kevin madden (857) 288-6390 <p><b>boston, ma -</b> today, governor (candidate full) issued the following statement on the passing of the reverend jerry falwell: </p><p>"an american who built and led a movement based on strong principles and strong faith has left us. he will be greatly missed, but the legacy of his important work will continue through his many ministries where he put his faith into action. </p><p>"ann and i have had the honor to talk and meet with reverend falwell and get to know him as a man of deep personal faith and commitment to helping those around him. he will be forever remembered."</p></span>



